# DSMC-hosted IAC physical-time loop control verification.
# The mass-Courant timestep is 5.0e-4 s, so a stop target of 1.1e-3 s
# should execute three voxel updates and stop at 1.5e-3 s.

voxel material carbon density 1800.0
voxel create solid slab nx 8 ny 4 nz 4 dx 1.0e-6 material carbon

source q1 constant 1.8 units kg/m2/s
iac stats 1
iac stats-style step time active-voxels deleted-voxels mass-fraction front
iac timestep mass/courant 0.5 source q1

variable keep internal 1
label ablate-loop
voxel ablate solid source q1 policy local face xlo delete yes
iac continue time 1.1e-3 variable keep
if "${keep} > 0" then "jump SELF ablate-loop"

iac set finaltime time
print "IAC_FINAL_TIME=${finaltime}" screen no

iac verify step exact "3" tolerance 0.01 absolute norm final
iac verify time exact "1.5e-3" tolerance 1.0e-12 absolute norm final
